David Canary https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Canary 0 David Hoyt Canary (August 25, 1938 – November 16, 2015) was an American actor. Canary is best known for his role as Adam Chandler in the television soap opera All My Children, for which he received sixteen Daytime Emmy Award nominations and won five times.
